      "span_text": "Based on the residual pressure, each ear was classified into 1 of 4 tubal function groups according to the methods of Elner et al. Group 1 ears equilibrated positive and negative pressures completely (residual pressure Ͻ10 daPa and Ͼ−10 daPa, respectively)."
